Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.39,0:00:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\N Just Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.60,0:00:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.71,0:00:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.92,0:00:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.72,0:00:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:01:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.44,0:01:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.75,0:01:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.56,0:01:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉財團\N藉著邀請和平的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.03,0:01:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為財團的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到人們的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令世界國家實現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.54,0:01:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面，在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反抗OZ殖民地式支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.88,0:01:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稱為白色獠牙的武裝市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.28,0:01:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在各個衛星紛紛起義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了獨立運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.52,0:01:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰亂的時代繼續進一步加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.29,0:01:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨大變動的一剎那即將出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.47,0:02:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的人請聽我講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特\N從今日起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.38,0:02:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為羅姆斐拉財團的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.21,0:02:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這並非為了羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.38,0:02:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了令世界的紛爭消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.15,0:02:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建立和平的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.19,0:02:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這是朝著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能和各位一起走的最好的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.69,0:02:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踏出的第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.19,0:02:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，請你們\N拋掉武器停止鬥爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.57,0:02:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位渴望的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.77,0:02:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該一定是相同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.57,0:02:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起朝著那未來前進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.24,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡宣佈除去\N世界紛爭之源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國家的門戶之見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確立把地球當作一個國家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.75,0:02:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[世界國家]宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三十九話\N[特洛瓦回歸戰場]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果建立了世界國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也就要換工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差勁的玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後會更加忙碌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.89,0:03:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為女王陛下的最強兵團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.27,0:03:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是下一次戰鬥正等待我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.34,0:03:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生你是士兵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一起走沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖國消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有要保護的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又失去戰鬥的意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就恢復和平便好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.51,0:04:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒理由這麼輕易就能得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是傑克斯特校嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，你是米利亞爾特大使嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了衛星市民的自由意顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺身而出的革命鬥士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙的坎斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.41,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只在衛星革命不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要在地球發起革命嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的玩笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.72,0:05:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是閃電伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.19,0:05:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜，我沒話和你們說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.66,0:05:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不信任我們或許也是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是繼承了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.73,0:05:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領導人希洛‧唯的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前也會\N作為山克王國的大使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自稱米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.94,0:05:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解過衛星的獨立吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.68,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.52,0:05:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你再次來宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.72,0:05:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的鋼彈一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和鋼彈一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.53,0:05:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，鋼彈是反抗的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.43,0:05:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要你和鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.61,0:06:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉著莉莉娜女王\N的世界國家宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無謂的紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將從我們的地球上消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那誠然是高興的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.76,0:06:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.89,0:06:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的責任並非就此履行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.89,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了我們曾保護他們的恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.30,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯示出反抗意思的叛亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要消滅這些叛賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.64,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令整個地球回復和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎?迪爾麥優侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.74,0:06:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼問題?偉列茲公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.71,0:06:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是羅姆斐拉財團的甚麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.32,0:06:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不大明白你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.52,0:06:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的新代表兼領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.16,0:06:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是莉莉娜女王嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.33,0:07:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾麥優侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.00,0:07:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你站在那裡說出今後的方針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.30,0:07:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得那非常不敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認為你也應該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和特列斯‧克修里那達一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.57,0:07:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這財團自動引退的應該不只我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.51,0:07:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我們和你不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能橫蠻地行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.08,0:07:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提議採用民主表決吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是合理的意見啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，為了避免重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,君主專制帶來的歷史性錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無意讓出現有的地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然，如果有必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有準備好隨時下台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你指現在不是那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣說能得你明白了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偉列茲公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果世界就此回復和平…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.60,0:08:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾麥優侯爵想維護自己的地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才全面擁立莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而令他自己的地位動搖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在，在羅姆斐拉財團之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜女王的支持者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也已經超過半數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.92,0:08:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們希望莉莉娜女王成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名副其實的世界國家君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.69,0:08:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桃樂絲小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為時代應該\N朝著正確方向移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.31,0:08:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?  五飛果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.88,0:09:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有他的生活方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.72,0:09:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不能強迫他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.32,0:09:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你來了也算值得慶幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.29,0:09:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為沒記憶的我沒甚麼作為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.43,0:09:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，和你們一起\N令我感到安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就此前去\N溫拿家的資源衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.61,0:09:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後在那裡替沙漠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行宇宙用最終調整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離很遠，拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要拜託你們的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.52,0:09:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.03,0:09:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由與和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家究竟怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子的我也是這樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.55,0:10:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.19,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒話和你們說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.96,0:10:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你始終不肯協助我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們自有主意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N你們以為我會上那種當嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.84,0:10:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.17,0:10:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們需要鋼彈作為象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很可惜啊，迪歐‧麥斯威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到鋼彈會成為敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別真的想惹怒我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想長命百歲的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.92,0:10:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點!走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希爾妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧他們找到這裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們神通廣大無處不曉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一定要離開這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要走嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.41,0:11:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，我不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.55,0:11:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再令妳和這城市有麻煩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.09,0:11:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以…和你一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.66,0:11:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有參加白色獠牙一途吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正也是為了衛星而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.77,0:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以回去軍隊再次戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪歐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.38,0:11:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得找到自己的生活方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹嘛要走回頭路啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.05,0:11:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留心聽我講，希爾妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不能信賴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.12,0:11:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們和OZ有相同的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.53,0:12:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這樣下去會毫無回報吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果參加白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.80,0:12:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就會被當作英雄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對那種東西沒興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.50,0:12:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠做死神就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨的戰鬥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.95,0:12:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，那是我們選擇了的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.95,0:12:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不可以把衛星捲入戰爭裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.96,0:12:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們太仁慈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼是世界國家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.24,0:13:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們以為那種事\N能騙到我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，西迪茲上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.21,0:13:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個真正渴望和平的領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.98,0:13:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種女孩怎會有那種力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.15,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是OZ，亦是羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.29,0:13:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看丟一直以來\N壓迫我們的實體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.26,0:13:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的衛星是獨立了的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使在令地球的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白那一點的意思上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一定要\N盡快完成這艘戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.74,0:13:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接收了的月面基地怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在茲巴洛夫MD工場裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大量比爾哥零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為我們白色獠牙的戰力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正穩定進行裝修了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武裝起來的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令這個衛星也被當作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ宇宙軍的駐軍基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.57,0:14:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而受到白色獠牙的攻擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種戰鬥最近屢見不鮮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個被毀嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙朝著錯誤的方向前進嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.98,0:14:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把武器帶來宇宙的\N是舊統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.78,0:14:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在衛星製造武器的是從前的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.42,0:14:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓迫及支配市民的是羅姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括今次白色獠牙的起義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.29,0:14:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是地球方面埋下的種子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.90,0:14:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被時代玩弄的事態就太可悲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.00,0:14:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從散播的種子長出來的芽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由誰來令它們凋謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜小姐想那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是自願投身羅姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.48,0:15:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要成為幫助她的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.91,0:15:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左翼推進器被毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不識別就攻擊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.19,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢隨便出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.76,0:15:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們見識\N我們宇宙軍的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士從敵人\N穿梭機裡出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.04,0:15:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用密集隊型迎擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左翼的MD消滅穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.04,0:15:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦\N你一個人去太魯莽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.48,0:15:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像曾經學過，我試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色陶拉斯?何方神聖?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厲…厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.33,0:16:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這部穿梭機數分鐘後就會自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開後馬上攻擊敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好遲純!沙漠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡就是極限嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諾茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.28,0:17:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?是鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.92,0:17:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙得到鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.99,0:17:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,散開!散開包圍他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.37,0:18:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾!你想做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部穿梭機要爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以這部沙漠鋼彈的推進器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會趕不及去特洛瓦那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.99,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰碰運氣!我要試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱薩琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.49,0:19:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對機械，你們真不像樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是好人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.13,0:19:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地獄死神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我要救曾毀掉你的傢伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.76,0:20:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?你忘了我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你珍貴的好朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說笑啊，說笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真沒趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.47,0:21:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪歐，你肯和我們一起戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.98,0:21:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，因為戰鬥的只有我們就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.32,0:21:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪歐‧麥斯威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.92,0:21:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我衷心感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別有太大期望比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.96,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我會馬上令你失望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.99,0:21:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那傢伙死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.59,0:21:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界國家和這種虛假的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.19,0:22:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就能被消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.20,0:22:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.20,0:22:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.74,0:22:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.09,0:22:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.09,0:22:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.09,0:22:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.09,0:22:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.59,0:22:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.09,0:23:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.59,0:23:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.09,0:23:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.09,0:23:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.42,0:23:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛計劃暗殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.26,0:23:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉財團的領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.16,0:23:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.29,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在財團內增加支持者的莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.56,0:23:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想朝著和平踏出第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.23,0:23:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，宇宙不了解地球的真意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.77,0:23:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,率領白色獠牙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.04,0:23:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.50,0:23:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣佈要肅清地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.31,0:23:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第四十話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.41,0:23:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的領導人
